byline.contributor: Charanna Alexander contributed reporting from Red Hook, Brooklyn.

lead_paragraph: Matthew Caws, of the band Nada Surf, and Emily Bidwell may have had an inkling of life ahead when they met 16 years ago at a Brooklyn record store.

headline.print_headline: The Atlantic Ocean Is No Obstacle
headline.main: For the Rock Star, Love Has Finally Landed
